{"tid":2171633,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日午 TINO’S PIZZA","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:58:02.000Z","uid":310853,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f85fc8646f0aa16e59af9867bff781b462652d4","tid":2171633,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"今日好撚慘 原本想試添福小食嘅漢堡包<br />\nGoogle咗今日冇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來平時仲要係兩點半先開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後諗住食Q1 第一郡嘅越式法包<br />\n點知行到過去 google睇錯咗<br />\n原來星期一都係冇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就行咗過去黃金嗰邊試TINO&rsquo;S PIZZA<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETPTuO2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETPTuO2.png&h=06b55a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4afH9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4afH9d.png&h=98201362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依個餅底我幾鍾意 比較薄身但都煙韌 啱我口味<br />\n但上面d料真係太少 依樣就真係麻麻地<br />\n對比起上嚟 長沙灣嘅DK PIZZA 趣意廚個PIZZA d料就足好多<br />\n湯就應該係粟米南瓜湯 都OK<br />\n薯格就淨係得兩塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LP3kUhE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLP3kUhE.png&h=835cbada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後佢比張嘢我 好似幾抵<br />\n不過下次有機會要試嘅話 就應該轉返試意大利麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/we3kUi7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwe3kUi7.png&h=84ea1911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最感動嘅係 今次終於有唔甜嘅飲品揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714020dfd4fe0ad28db78b724f4e6ac28037728f","tid":2171633,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim